msgid "Split the inventory into a few groups, considering that the configuration of hosts belonging to a group will be identical."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: article_openscap.xml:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the standard or profile you plan to implement. For example, you can use the &disa; STIG, the &pcidss; (PCI-DSS) or the &hipaa; (HIPAA)."
msgstr ""

