msgid "Deselect the rules that you do not want in the custom profile. For example, you can deselect the following rule: <literal>Record Events that Modify the System's Discretionary Access Controls - chmod</literal> ."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: article_openscap.xml:814
