#. Tag: title
#: article_openscap.xml:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule ID"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: article_openscap.xml:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "For example, <literal>xccdf_org.ssgproject.content_rule_package_aide_installed</literal> ."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: article_openscap.xml:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid "After determining the security policy and profile, use <command>oscap xccdf eval</command> to perform an evaluation against them. For example, to evaluate the profile <literal>xccdf_org.ssgproject.content_profile_stig</literal> and generate an HTML report, you can use the following command format:"
